    },
    "e05_n03": {
      "id": "e05_n03",
      "speaker": "MAYA",
      "events": [
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 2600
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "Grant handled security. Head of Not Dying, he called himself.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03.event0.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 3600
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "He said it as a joke, but Grant had this way of joking like he was writing his own job description.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03.event3.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 3600
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "Rivera managed logistics. Park and Owens were stuck in the lower sectors.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03.event1.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 3000
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "Nobody liked the lower sectors. Park pretended he did. Owens called him a liar every morning.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03.event2.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 4200
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "Park once said the lower sectors had 'character.'",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03.event9.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 3600
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "Owens said mold also has character.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03.event11.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 3300
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "They argued for twenty minutes.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03.event13.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 3000
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "Then she brought him coffee.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03.event15.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 900
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 3800
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "People were like that on ECHO.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03.event18.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 3600
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "Annoying. Alive.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03.event20.text"
        }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "ask_about_hale_role",
          "text": "WHAT WAS HALE'S ROLE?",
          "effects": {
            "mayaTrust": 3,
            "danger": 1
          },
          "nextNodeId": "e05_n03_hale",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03.choice0.text"
        },
        {
          "id": "scan_manifest_systems",
          "text": "SCAN SUPPORT SYSTEM RECORDS.",
          "effects": {
            "signalStrength": -1,
            "danger": 1
          },
          "nextNodeId": "e05_n04",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03.choice1.text"
        },
        {
          "id": "ask_who_you_miss",
          "text": "WHO DO YOU MISS THE MOST?",
          "effects": {
            "mayaTrust": 4,
            "morale": -2
          },
          "nextNodeId": "e05_n03_miss",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03.dc.choice0.text"
        }
      ]
    },
    "e05_n03_hale": {
      "id": "e05_n03_hale",
      "speaker": "MAYA",
      "events": [
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 3400
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "Hale kept the station breathing.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03_hale.event0.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 4200
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "Power, relay routing, pressure control, emergency doors. If something opened or closed, Hale probably had a way into it.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03_hale.event1.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 3800
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "Ethan could open almost any door on the station.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03_hale.event5.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 4200
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "The strange thing is that he was terrible at opening up to people.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03_hale.event7.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 3800
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "He corrected reports in red.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03_hale.event10.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 3200
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "Digital reports. Red comments. On a station.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03_hale.event12.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 3600
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "I told him that was hostile.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03_hale.event14.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 3400
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "He said accuracy was not a friendship contest.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03_hale.event16.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "pause",
          "duration": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 4200
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "That's why I don't like hearing his voice in places it shouldn't be.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03_hale.event2.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 4200
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "Because the real Hale was hard to like sometimes.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03_hale.event21.text"
        },
        {
          "type": "typing",
          "duration": 3600
        },
        {
          "type": "message",
          "text": "But he was ours.",
          "textKey": "episode_05.e05_n03_hale.event23.text"
        }
      ],
      "nextNodeId": "e05_n04"
    },
    "e05_n04": {
